    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_524231">We had a house rule in our D3.5 campaigns that divided the exp cost for items amongst all players in the group. So instead of just the caster paying it, everyone paid a part for it. Works amazingly well.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
